OL,7,FRebekah Vardy lost her high-profile
OL,8,Flibel case against Coleen Rooney in
OL,9,FJuly 2022, when Mrs Justice Steyn
OL,10,Fruled Mrs Rooney's viral social media
OL,11,Fpost accusing Mrs Vardy of leaking her
OL,12,Fprivate information to the press was
OL,13,F"substantially true".
OL,15,FIn October of the same year, the judge
OL,16,Fruled Mrs Vardy should pay 90% of Mrs
OL,17,FRooney's legal costs.
