OL,7,FRobin Dunne, Mrs Rooney's lawyer, said
OL,8,FMrs Vardy's team had accrued
OL,9,F"unreasonable and disproportionate"
OL,10,Fcosts before the trial.
OL,12,FMrs Vardy's lawyers are opposing the
OL,13,Fbid to reduce the costs bill. Jamie
OL,14,FCarpenter KC, for Mrs Vardy, said
OL,15,Fthere was "barely a day" when her
OL,16,Flawyers were not working at the time,
OL,17,Fincluding "on Christmas Day."
