OL,7,F"This was work that absolutely had to
OL,8,Fbe done and it was a huge amount of
OL,9,Fwork," Mr Carpenter told the Court,
OL,10,Fadding that "no one was costs
OL,11,Fbuilding."
OL,13,FThe case is being heard before a
OL,14,Fspecialist costs judge, Andrew Gordon-
OL,15,FSaker, and is set to include on
OL,16,FWednesday.
OL,18,FThe judge will assess the true costs
OL,19,Fand expenses incurred during civil
OL,20,Fcases and rule on how much successful
OL,21,Fparties can recover.
